1.Client buys ticket to travel from source to destination
2.Then he can board any bus to reach the destination from source
3.A ticket will be valid for only one day
4.Once ticket has be bought by clientManager it will be added to a queue in DB
1. Conductor scans ticket from clientManager app, then sends acknowledgment to adminManager
2. Admin then makes the ticket invalid for future, and stores it in history

